{"tid":131749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港Uber有保險公司提供第三保","createTime":"2017-02-23T09:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-24T09:59:32.000Z","uid":33890,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8924c132361f4b6e00c181c19e6dc8b81616b2","tid":131749,"uid":33890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:29:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170223/56343579\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170223%2F56343579&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ9Wu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=62275681\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170223%2F56343579&h=38ef6149\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170223/56343579</a><br />\n香港Uber今日宣布，成功獲一間本地保險公司提供第三者保險，保單最高賠償額為一億港元。這是首次有保險公司肯為香港Uber提供第三保。<br />\n<br />\nUber表示，美亞保險香港有限公司（AIG Insurance Hong Kong Limited）願意提供團體汽車共乘（ride-share）責任保險，為 Uber 在港所有車程的乘客及涉及的第三者提供額外保障。每宗涉及乘客或第三者身體受傷或死亡事故，最高賠償額為一億港元，保單有效期由去年10月17日起至今年9月30日。<br />\n<br />\nDC9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30361fb9921bd52705b57a83a460993be9b5409","tid":131749,"uid":2090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:34:04.000Z","msg":"即係之前冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"b65eb1a3d2feda138971f88637db1823cfb9f917","tid":131749,"uid":68884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係之前冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n你個名有聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4640ccc72774af997066f1a875b06c57545cb5ac","tid":131749,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係之前冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n冇 唔係的士邊有呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff378959787f8321b69cd214266751362dd24cdc","tid":131749,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T09:50:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1cced5249c8647d3691ff5c1a4d5040c4e70865","tid":131749,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T10:52:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係之前冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a902a4b44ffeb7347706b5072e46e75c7f7e4373","tid":131749,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:02:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實uber咁撚多人投資，大把資金<br />\n做self-insurance得唔得？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁要每日開車前查定 Uber 有幾多 Asset 你再判斷佢賠唔賠得起.   Uber 唔係九巴, 佢涉足全世界. 今日可以有 30b 資產聽日係 0.  九巴你唔掂班仆街係香港都叫搵到人屌.<br />\n<br />\n當年係高登講撚左班柒頭無保險, 但係呢 D 表面上保.<br />\n如果香港判定佢係白牌非法最後保唔保先?<br />\n<br />\n有班撚樣話唔怕有咩保險基金,重撚自私叫其他人幫手找數 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7276ede2705bcfc3c33d57416e53a0be71f6c638","tid":131749,"uid":2090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>即係之前冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n冇 唔係的士邊有呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢之前好撚大聲話有第三者保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb6dfb99ea0149f1f233f921dc8507261b1f4fa","tid":131749,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>即係之前冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n冇 唔係的士邊有呢樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢之前好撚大聲話有第三者保險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n「香港保險業聯會回覆本網指，保險公司的原則是不能保障任何非法事項，故此透過Uber程式接載客人的白牌車司機，不受第三者保險保障。一旦發生意外，乘客只能追究涉事司機。為Uber服務的私家車須領有合法商業牌照，才能受第三者保險保障，聯會亦相信有合法的出租車、房車為Uber服務。對於Uber網上列明的保險條款，聯會指當中只提到第三保適用於美國各州，但並無指明此保障適用於香港，故擔心保險未必涵蓋到香港。」-之前拉Uber司機果排，某X場新聞報導節錄<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUber自己講果隻第三者保險唔適用於香港，仲有呢次所謂「受保」都剩係表明上受保<br />\n<br />\nUber應該指出黎唔好誤導人入行先啱"}]}